; SNAPKITTY RESONANCE ASSEMBLY — canonical sovereign program
; Pipeline: E → A → A → C → D → G → F → H
; Meaning:  ENTER → LOAD → LOAD → COMPARE → BRANCH → SIGNAL → FREEZE → HALT

; Enter the resonance scope / deed boundary
E field_core

